    About this item

    • Adaptive Noise Cancelling with Smart Ambient
    • Adaptive Noise Cancelling means zero distractions when it's time to focus on your studiesor get your groove on. And if you want to hear the world around you without removing your headphones, Ambient Aware and TalkThru sharpen the sounds of your surroundings or voices. Easily activate these Ambient Sound Control modes through the JBL Headphones app.
    • Bluetooth 5.3 with LE Audio*
    • Wirelessly stream high-quality JBL Pure Bass Sound from your smartphone with the help of the latest Bluetooth technology. Optimize the Bluetooth performance with the Smart Audio & Video feature in the JBL Headphones app by selecting the Audio (for the best sound quality) or the Video (for an optimal gaming and video output) modes. *Available via OTA update at a later stage.
    • JBL Pure Bass Sound
    • JBL Tune 670NC headphones feature renowned JBL Pure Bass soundthe same that powers the most famous music venues all around the world.
    • Customize your listening experience
    • Download the free JBL Headphones App to tailor the sound to your taste by choosing one of the pre-set EQ modes or adjusting the EQ curve according to your content, your style, your taste. Voice Prompts in your language guide you through the Tune 670NCs other features.
    • Hands-free calls with VoiceAware
    • Easily control your sound and manage your calls from your headphones with the convenient buttons on the ear-cup. Hear your voice while you're talking, with the help of VoiceAware.

      • Product Description

      Lightness, comfort, and great sound. With the JBL Tune 670NC Adaptive Noise Cancelling wireless headphones, youve got all three. With up to 70 hours of battery life, the JBL Tune 670NC will get you through your week, with no need of a top-up. And if you do need a quick recharge, 5 minutes gets you an extra 3 hours of music, or just plug in the detachable headphone cable to keep your flow going. The JBL Tune 670NC connect with two Bluetooth devices simultaneously, so youll never miss a call while watching a movie on your tablet. With the free JBL Headphones app, you can tailor the sound to suit your taste. And voice prompts in your language will guide you through the features. Manage your calls and your voice assistant hassle-free right from your phone, and use VoiceAware to hear yourself when youre speaking. All this, plus you can choose the color that best represents your vibe.

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • Iris Allen
        4.0 out of 5 stars Love!!
        Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2025
        Color: PurpleVerified Purchase
        I dont know where to begin.
        I was more interested in a different JBL model, but they didnt come in my favorite color lol these match all of my accessories! The most important thing for me was an aux port and noise cancellation so I could use them for work and for home. These had everything I needed! The sound is spectacular. These are relatively comfortable and I wear them all day. I never sweat even after 8 hours of wear. I do wear glasses so its inevitable that they get uncomfortable, but the swivel of the headset actually helps so much.

        I use them for music, work, and gaming! At work, I make phone calls and I use them with Microsoft Teams with no problems. The sound quality for calls is really good and it is truly noise cancelling for both parties. The sound is incredibly immersive while gaming. Playing Detroit Become Human on my PC while having these paired is a completely different experience and Im obsessed. Listening to music is an experience I have never had before. The sound quality is phenomenal and I truly love these headphones.

        The talk thru feature does not work. My husband has AirPods Pro 2 and they automatically adjust the sound level when speaking. Talk thru should work that way, but it doesnt. The ambient sounds also does not work. The active noise cancellation does work. The other two features, I dont really care about. It was just worth noting. (I dont like earbuds, thats why I dont have AirPods. I mentioned them to compare the features). I dont like that the headphones automatically connect to any device that it has been paired to if the device is on and my headphones are on. Even if I go into the Bluetooth settings and select disconnect, once I power off and then power back on my headphones, they automatically reconnect. I like that you can manage many settings, including power, from the app, but it would be nice to also be able to manage devices that you are currently connected to. I will say that the range is pretty far.

        I apologize for the long review. I always appreciate thorough reviews and figured I would leave one since I use my headphones in several ways.

      • Adaptive Noise Cancelling means zero distractions when it's time to focus on your studiesor get your groove on. And if you want to hear the world around you without removing your headphones, Ambient Aware and TalkThru sharpen the sounds of your surroundings or voices. Easily activate these Ambient Sound Control modes through the JBL Headphones app.
      • Bluetooth 5.3 with LE Audio*
      • Wirelessly stream high-quality JBL Pure Bass Sound from your smartphone with the help of the latest Bluetooth technology. Optimize the Bluetooth performance with the Smart Audio & Video feature in the JBL Headphones app by selecting the Audio (for the best sound quality) or the Video (for an optimal gaming and video output) modes. *Available via OTA update at a later stage.
      • JBL Pure Bass Sound
      • JBL Tune 670NC headphones feature renowned JBL Pure Bass soundthe same that powers the most famous music venues all around the world.
      • Customize your listening experience
      • Download the free JBL Headphones App to tailor the sound to your taste by choosing one of the pre-set EQ modes or adjusting the EQ curve according to your content, your style, your taste. Voice Prompts in your language guide you through the Tune 670NCs other features.
      • Hands-free calls with VoiceAware
      • Easily control your sound and manage your calls from your headphones with the convenient buttons on the ear-cup. Hear your voice while you're talking, with the help of VoiceAware.

      Product Description

      Lightness, comfort, and great sound. With the JBL Tune 670NC Adaptive Noise Cancelling wireless headphones, youve got all three. With up to 70 hours of battery life, the JBL Tune 670NC will get you through your week, with no need of a top-up. And if you do need a quick recharge, 5 minutes gets you an extra 3 hours of music, or just plug in the detachable headphone cable to keep your flow going. The JBL Tune 670NC connect with two Bluetooth devices simultaneously, so youll never miss a call while watching a movie on your tablet. With the free JBL Headphones app, you can tailor the sound to suit your taste. And voice prompts in your language will guide you through the features. Manage your calls and your voice assistant hassle-free right from your phone, and use VoiceAware to hear yourself when youre speaking. All this, plus you can choose the color that best represents your vibe.
